===Cinemas===
Bern has several dozen cinemas. As is customary in German Switzerland, films are generally in German. Some films in select cinemas are shown in their original language with German and French subtitles.

===Film festivals===
* [[Shnit international shortfilmfestival]] shnit International Shortfilmfestival, held annually in early October.
* [[Queersicht]]&amp;nbsp;– gay and lesbian film festival, held annually in the second week of November.

